The git repository is created from original project on
http://sourceforge.net/projects/hr-xsl to remove dependency on ant-1.8
since it is not part of ubuntu 10.04 and mac os 10.6.4 
Number of commits were cherry-picked to branch ant-1.7

AUTHORS file sets names for git svn, although the original project is 
inactive http://sourceforge.net/news/?group_id=50922&id=282908
